OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FExtensive low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fslowly lifting and thinning, with
OL,7,Fbrighter spells possible, especially
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Mainly dry,
OL,9,Falthough an increasing chance of
OL,10,Fshowery rain through the afternoon.
OL,11,FFeeling milder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning drier again during
OL,14,FMonday evening with variable cloud
OL,15,Famounts. Thickest cloud across western
OL,16,Fareas with occasional rain or showers
OL,17,Flikely.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
